00:17:59,284 --> 00:18:01,329
[BUZZER IN DISTANCE]

556
00:18:01,353 --> 00:18:04,198
[CLOCK TICKING]

557
00:18:04,222 --> 00:18:05,433
PAULA: You staring at that clock's

